    "Metadata": {
        "Id": "75c31f51-1376-4da5-a88b-b2e6bac9c7cf",
        "Type": "usercreated",
        "Title": "The Code of the Shinobi, From L",
        "Location": "LOCATION_HOKKAIDO",
        "PublicId": "110285950640",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/Hokkaido/_scene_snowcrane.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository c4d3d686-04d2-492f-ae09-25291e71eb06).Image",
        "Description": "Good Evening, 47.\r\rJust because the ICA has been shut down doesn&apos;t mean the agents have lost their ways. Four members of the Yakuza terrorist group have been found to be ex-ICA agents who didn&apos;t want to stop killing people. The Yakuza are infamous for performing acts of terrorism while donning the outfit of the Shinobi and follow a code of (dis) honor known as the Shinobi Code. How about we turn their code against them?\r\rYour friend until the end,\rL",
        "GameVersion": "8.22.0.0",
